# OpenAi + Flutter

# Description:

It is simple integration of OpenAI Apis in Flutter using the http request where the speech is converted to text and then sent to the OpenApi Api to get the prompt with output in the form of Images or Chat or Text using DALL-E api or Chat api in OpenAI!!


## Getting Started

Step 1: --> cd dir 
        --> git clone https://github.com/Raghav-995/openaiflutter.git

Step2: --> add the OpenAI key in openaiflutter/openai/key.dart file where you need to add your key for value const # openAIAPIKey = 'Your OpenApi Key';

Step3: --> flutter pub upgrade or flutter pub get

step4: --> flutter run

# Building Apk

Step5: --> Flutter build apk --split-per-abi



